title: AC - Attack of the Blogs Mixtape
description:
On one day, Staten Island's 'AC' dropped 20 exclusive freestyles, one for each of the top 20 hip-hop blogs, this changed the mixtape game in a way where Blogs actually are now the new 'Mixtape' .. Check out this upload & be sure to watch out for Attack of the Blogs Pt. 2, which is promised to be even bigger than the original.

If you never heard of AC, all you have to do is google him, he be also best known for his 2008 underground smash, 'New Soul' which samples Yael Naim's hit single which was made popular during Apple's MacBook Air ad campaign.
